# fin-llama3.1-8b Modelfile for Ollama
#
# Model: us4/fin-llama3.1-8b (LLaMA 3.1 8B fine-tuned with LoRA on financial news)
# Source: https://huggingface.co/us4/fin-llama3.1-8b
# GGUF:   model-q4_k_m.gguf (4.92GB, pre-quantized Q4_K_M)
# Download: https://huggingface.co/us4/fin-llama3.1-8b/resolve/main/model-q4_k_m.gguf
#
# License: "[More Information Needed]" per HuggingFace listing — verify before production use.
#
# Usage:
#   1. Download the GGUF weights:
#      wget https://huggingface.co/us4/fin-llama3.1-8b/resolve/main/model-q4_k_m.gguf
#   2. Place the file at the path specified in FROM below (or update the path)
#   3. Create the model in Ollama:
#      ollama create fin-llama3.1:8b-finance -f deploy/fin-llama.Modelfile
#
# Memory footprint: ~4.92GB for this model. On the Mac Mini M4 16GB, this leaves room
# for llama3.1:8b (~5GB) alongside it, with ~6GB for the OS and mistral.
# Recommended: set OLLAMA_MAX_LOADED_MODELS=2 to keep fin-llama and llama3.1:8b hot.
#
# No TEMPLATE directive needed — Ollama handles the standard LLaMA 3.1 chat format natively.

FROM /path/to/model-q4_k_m.gguf

PARAMETER temperature 0.15
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER num_ctx 4096
